			<A NAME="STOSW">&nbsp;</A>
</TD>
</TR>





<TR>
<TD>
<FONT FACE="Courier">
STOSW
</FONT>
</TD>
<TD>No operands</TD>
<TD>

Store word in AX into ES:[DI]. Update DI.<BR><BR>Algorithm:
<BR><BR>
<FONT FACE="Courier">
<UL>
<LI>ES:[DI] = AX<BR></LI>
<LI>if DF = 0 then
	<UL>
	<LI>DI = DI + 2</LI>
	</UL>
	else
	<UL>
	<LI>DI = DI - 2</LI>
	</UL>
</LI>
</UL>
</FONT>
Example:
<PRE><FONT FACE="Courier">
ORG 100h

LEA DI, a1
MOV AX, 1234h
MOV CX, 5

REP STOSW

RET

a1 DW 5 dup(0)</FONT></PRE>

